'''Traveller's Tales''' is a British videogame developer. It co-operates through videogames with ''The Lego Group'', the company that creates [[Lego]] games. It has developed the [[Lego The Lord of the Rings: The Video Game]] (2012) and the [[Lego The Hobbit: The Video Game|Lego The Hobbit]] (2014) with [[Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment]].
